<body>
Reports all the arguments except for the first expression that does not evaluate to NULL in COALESCE functions.
<p>Example (MySQL):</p>
<pre><code>SELECT COALESCE(NULL, NULL, NULL, 42, NULL, 'string') as a;</code></pre>
<p>The first NOT NULL argument is <code>42</code>, all other arguments will be grayed out.</p>
